d with the British actress  Dawn Addams  (  1930–1985 ), the British comedienne  Dawn French  (  b. 1957 ), and the American singer  Dawn Upshaw  (  b. 1960 )."]}]},{"name":"Prytherch","type":"LAST","attribution":"Dictionary of Family Names in Britain and Ireland © University of the West of England 2016","meanings":["Welsh:  see  Prothero  ."],"variants":[{"name":"Prothero","meanings":["Welsh: Anglicized form of Welsh <i>ap Rhydderch</i> ‘son of<i>Rhydderch</i>’ (see   Roderick  )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Sir Vawn Prytherch Prute was born in 1089, in Wales, United Kingdom as the son of Sir Jean Perout Proute Prute. He had at least 1 son with Marged Verch Cadivor Vawr."},"et":{"1089–":"1089–Surnud","1089–Male":"1089–Surnud","1070–Female":"1070–Surnud","1150–1210":"1150–1210","1046–1120":"1046–1120","1046":"1046","1089":"1089","1210":"1210","1120":"1120","1150":"1150","1070":"1070","Somerset, England":"Somerset, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Wales":"Wales, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1089–":"1089–Kuollut","1089–Male":"1089–Kuollut","1070–Female":"1070–Kuollut","1150–1210":"1150–1210","1046–1120":"1046–1120","1046":"1046","1089":"1089","1210":"1210","1120":"1120","1150":"1150","1070":"1070","Somerset, England":"Somerset, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Wales":"Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1089–":"1089–Décédé","1089–Male":"1089–Décédé","1070–Female":"1070–Décédée","1150–1210":"1150–1210","1046–1120":"1046–1120","1046":"1046","1089":"1089","1210":"1210","1120":"1120","1150":"1150","1070":"1070","Somerset, England":"Somerset, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Wales":"Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Sir Vawn Prytherch Prute est né en 1089, à Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni, fils de Sir Jean Perout Proute Prute. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Marged Verch Cadivor Vawr."},"de":{"1089–":"1089–Verstorben","1089–Male":"1089–Verstorben","1070–Female":"1070–Verstorben","1150–1210":"1150–1210","1046–1120":"1046–1120","1046":"1046","1089":"1089","1210":"1210","1120":"1120","1